1.Updating ESP-IDF  

 The esp-idf version number I am using is esp-idf-v3.0.2.

This is the download link

https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/releases/download/v3.0.2/esp-idf-v3.0.2.zip

2.Updating Toolchain

The toolchain I use is  xtensa-esp32-elf-linux64-1.22.0-80-g6c4433a-5.2.0.tar.gz

Here is the download link

https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/v3.0.2/get-started/linux-setup.html
